<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head'); %>
  
</head>
<body class="flex bg-dark">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <header>
      <%- include('../partials/header'); %>
    </header>
    <main class="content">
      <div class="container" style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <h1 style="color: rgb(190, 187, 187)">About this website...</h1>
        <p>Welcome to my website! I am passionate about helping individuals find their dream jobs. With the job search feature, you can easily search for job listings based on title and location, and explore detailed job descriptions and related information.</p>
        <p>Our goal is to provide a user-friendly and efficient platform to streamline the job search process. Whether you are a recent graduate, a career changer, or simply looking for new opportunities, we strive to connect you with relevant job openings.</p>
        <p>Feel free to explore the job listings, save your favorite jobs, and create your personalized account to manage your saved jobs. We are here to assist you in your job search journey and help you take the next step towards a fulfilling career.</p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <%- include('../partials/footer'); %>
    </footer>
  </div>
  
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>


<style>
  main {
    background-color: black;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }
  
  h1, p {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 30px;
  }

  li {
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .container {
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .jumbotron {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px rgb(164, 159, 159), -5px -5px 50px rgb(172, 170, 170);
  }

  .form-row {
    margin-top: 15px;
  }

  .btn-custom {
    background-color: #4669f5;
    border-radius: 15px;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .btn-custom:hover {
    background-color: #bababa;
    color: white;
  }

  .card {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    background-color: rgb(31, 30, 30);
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: white;
  }

  .card-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    color: white;
  }

  html,
  body {
    height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* New CSS for the footer */
  footer {
    position: fixed;
    height: 35px;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #333;
    padding: 10px; /* Decreased padding */
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .container ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  /* Increased margin between paragraph and footer */
  main .container {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }
</style>
</body>
</html>
